hristos", "author_caption": "Austin, Texas", "card_link": "", "card_color_scheme": "scheme-2", "color_scheme_bg_fix": false}}, "column_standard_zQNXJh": {"type": "column_standard", "settings": {"image": "shopify://shop_images/67d858e06e8af838f858ef13.png", "image_ratio": "adapt", "image_width": 100, "rating_stars": 5, "title": "", "heading_tag": "h3", "text": "<p>I'm thoroughly impressed with these chews They're incredibly durable, made from natural ingredients, and perfect for heavy chewers. My dog absolutely loves them, and I appreciate the company's transparency regarding the ingredients. This brand has won me over, and I'll definitely be a loyal customer from now</p>", "author_name": "Alex Williams", "author_caption": "Dallas, TX", "card_link": "", "card_color_scheme": "scheme-2", "color_scheme_bg_fix": false}}, "column_standard_EcUJHc": {"type": "column_standard", "settings": {"image": "shopify://shop_images/yakcheese_review.webp", "image_ratio": "adapt", "image_width": 100, "rating_stars": 5, "title": "", "heading_tag": "h3", "text": "<p>Great value for the price! One chew keeps my dog busy for days, and I\u2019m confident I\u2019m giving him something healthy and safe. Unlike the treats that vanished in minutes, these yak chews actually last and keep him satisfied. My dog and I couldn\u2019t be happier.</p>", "author_name": "Sam Davis", "author_caption": "San Francisco, California", "card_link": "", "card_color_scheme": "scheme-2", "color_scheme_bg_fix": false}}, "column_standard_wEPgzG": {"type": "column_standard", "settings": {"image": "shopify://shop_images/yakcheesereview_2.webp", "image_ratio": "adapt", "image_width": 100, "rating_stars": 5, "title": "", "heading_tag": "h3", "text": "<p>Our dogs are enjoying their new treats and toys. The bones last a good while our puppy chews for hours on them</p>", "author_name": "Casey Brown", "author_caption": "Denver, Colorado", "card_link": "", "card_color_scheme": "scheme-2", "color_scheme_bg_fix": false}}, "column_standard_qdQYXf": {"type": "column_standard", "disabled": true, "settings": {"image_ratio": "adapt", "image_width": 100, "rating_stars": 5, "title": "<strong>User-friendly website</strong>", "heading_tag": "h3", "text": "<p>Easy to navigate and make purchases. A hassle-free shopping experience with clear descriptions and transparent pricing.</p>", "author_name": "Riley Wilson", "author_caption": "Boston, Massachusetts", "card_link": "", "card_color_scheme": "scheme-5", "color_scheme_bg_fix": false}}, "column_standard_b7rzwP": {"type": "column_standard", "settings": {"image_ratio": "adapt", "image_width": 100, "rating_stars": 5, "title": "Testimonial", "heading_tag": "h3", "text": "<p>Include a review of the product or collection left by a customer. Or perhaps it's a review of your store as whole.</p>", "author_name": "Jane Doe", "author_caption": "Director, Company name", "card_link": "", "card_color_scheme": "scheme-2", "color_scheme_bg_fix": false}}}, "block_order": ["column_standard_MK3xac", "column_standard_AfDPxB", "column_standard_zQNXJh", "column_standard_EcUJHc", "column_standard_wEPgzG", "column_standard_qdQYXf", "column_standard_b7rzwP"], "custom_css": [".card-padding {padding-top: 0px;}", "h2 {color: #2b1408; font-size: 42px;}"], "name": "Review Section", "settings": {"review_style": "star", "rating_size": 3, "heading_style": "text-body", "card_heading_size": "h5", "card_text_size": "t4", "author_line": true, "desktop_section_height": 90, "mobile_section_height": 180, "column_alignment": "left", "text_vertical_alignment": "justify-center", "content_padding": 2, "desktop_layout": "carousel", "mobile_layout": "carousel", "columns_desktop": "3", "columns_desktop_scale": true, "full_width": false, "image_overlay_opacity": 0, "content_max_width": "m", "desktop_heading_alignment": "center", "mobile_heading_alignment": "left", "title": "<strong>Approved By Dog and Parents</strong>", "italic_convert": "", "heading_size": "h1", "text": "<p>With Over 8000+ Reviews</p>", "text_size": "t2", "view_all_link": "", "view_all_text": "", "view_all_text_size": "t3", "color_scheme": "scheme-2", "star_color": "#ea0707", "card_shadow": true, "line_separator": "", "top_padding": "pt-s15", "bottom_padding": "pb-s15", "visibility": "", "hide_when_empty": false, "show_at_specific_time_of_day": false, "show_time_morning": true, "show_time_afternoon": true, "show_time_evening": true, "show_time_night": true, "heading_tag": "h2"}}, "featured_blog_fzWQaG": {"type": "featured-blog", "custom_css": ["h2 {font-weight: bold; font-size: 42px;}"], "name": "Dog Behavior Blogs", "settings": {"blog": "dog-behavior", "posts_to_show": 12, "show_image": true, "show_date": false, "show_author": false, "show_reading_estimate": false, "show_first_tag": false, "excerpt_mode": "short", "blog_card_featured": "", "featured_excerpt_mode": "none", "desktop_layout": "carousel", "mobile_layout": "carousel", "columns_desktop": "4", "full_width": false, "content_max_width": "m", "desktop_heading_alignment": "center", "mobile_heading_alignment": "left", "title": "Dog Behavior Tips", "italic_convert": "", "heading_size": "h1", "text": "<p>Read our most recent articles and suggestions on dogs behavior and how to manage them. </p>", "text_size": "t3", "show_view_all_link": true, "view_all_text": "View more", "view_all_text_size": "t3", "view_all_card_visibility": "off", "view_all_card_text": "Keep reading", "color_scheme": "scheme-1", "view_all_color_scheme": "scheme-1", "line_separator": "", "top_padding": "pt-s", "bottom_padding": "pb-s", "visibility": "", "hide_when_empty": false, "show_at_specific_time_of_day": false, "show_time_morning": true, "show_time_afternoon": true, "show_time_evening": true, "show_time_night": true, "heading_tag": "h2"}}, "faqs_KDWjwK": {"type": "faqs", "blocks": {"faq_item_hxgjjh": {"type": "faq_item", "settings": {"question": "What are Himalayan Yak Chews?", "answer": "<p>Prime Pet Food Yak Chews are traditional Himalayan dog treats made from yak and cow milk. They are completely natural, free from chemicals and preservatives, and crafted using time-tested methods from the Himalayan region. Their hard texture makes them long-lasting and highly satisfying for dogs.</p>"}}, "faq_item_Qprh7Q": {"type": "faq_item", "settings": {"question": "Where do your chews come from?", "answer": "<p>Our chews are inspired by an ancient Himalayan recipe, originally made for human consumption. Today, we bring this authentic process to your dogs\u2014using high-quality milk sourced from free-grazing animals and crafted into a safe, nutritious chew.</p>"}}, "faq_item_hkEemN": {"type": "faq_item", "settings": {"question": "How are Prime Pet Food chews made?", "answer": "<p>Our chews go through a careful process:</p><ol><li>Fresh milk is collected and pasteurized</li><li>It is turned into dense cheese</li><li>Naturally aged for hardness and durability</li><li>Cut, cleaned, and inspected</li><li>Slowly dried for long shelf life</li></ol><p><br/>This process creates a healthy, long-lasting chew your dog will love.</p>"}}, "faq_item_JAEqRG": {"type": "faq_item", "settings": {"question": "Are yak chews safe for dogs?", "answer": "<p>Yes \u2014 they are safe and digestible. Unlike raw milk, the cheese-making process removes most lactose and fats, making it easier on your dog\u2019s stomach. As with any chew, supervision is recommended.</p>"}}, "faq_item_EcLKzx": {"type": "faq_item", "settings": {"question": "Do yak chews cause weight gain?", "answer": "<p>Yak chews are high in protein and nutrients like calcium and vitamins. While they are not inherently fattening, moderation is key. They are a healthier alternative to many processed treats.</p>"}}, "faq_item_Ffeqk7": {"type": "faq_item", "settings": {"question": "How do I choose the right size for my dog?", "answer": "<ul><li><strong>Small</strong>: for dogs up to 15 lbs</li><li><strong>Medium</strong>: for dogs up to 35 lbs</li><li><strong>Large</strong>: for dogs up to 55 lbs</li><li><strong>Extra Large</strong>: for dogs up to 85 lbs</li><li><strong>Jumbo</strong>: for dogs above 85<br/><br/>Choosing the right size ensures safety and longer chew time.</li></ul>"}}}, "block_order": ["faq_item_hxgjjh", "faq_item_Qprh7Q", "faq_item_hkEemN", "faq_item_JAEqRG", "faq_item_EcLKzx", "faq_item_Ffeqk7"], "custom_css": ["h2 {margin-top: 0px; font-size: 42px;}"], "name": "Accordion FAQ", "settings": {"eyebrow": "Common Questions", "heading": "Everything You Need to Know", "subtext": "Have more questions? We are here to help.", "accordion_mode": false, "first_open": false, "list_max_width": 760, "padding_top": 64, "padding_bottom": 64, "bg_color": "#ffffff", "eyebrow_color": "#c8943e", "heading_color": "#24130d", "subtext_color": "#8b7d6b", "item_bg": "#ffffff", "item_border": "#ede5d8", "item_border_open": "#2d4a3e", "question_color": "#2c2c2c", "answer_color": "#8b7d6b", "icon_color": "#2d4a3e", "icon_bg": "#f0f7f3", "icon_color_open": "#ffffff", "icon_bg_open": "#d2632e"}}, "chew_analyzer_hero": {"type": "chew-analyzer", "settings": {"display_mode": "hero", "show_section_heading": true, "heading": "How Long Will This Last For <em>YOUR</em> Dog?", "subtitle": "Our AI analyzes your dog's breed, size, and chewing style to estimate exactly how long our premium Himalayan yak chews will keep them happily occupied.", "cta_text": "Analyze Your Dog", "cta_link": "/collections/all", "top_padding": "pt-medium", "bottom_padding": "pb-medium"}}}, "order": ["hero_banner_Bx4FFT", "ypc_hero_slider_bxtUGx", "ypc_scrolling_mPNmJb", "video_carousel_xyUX4h", "featured_products_hQf3re", "chew_analyzer_hero", "icons_with_text_VbFdBf", "manufacturing_process_6jhGF6", "two_treats_in_one_QnDL8z", "bonus_treat_steps_hjaHTi", "our_story_taxeQz", "comparison_table_zn368V", "comparison_C3zMAU", "testimonials_FL97cf", "featured_blog_fzWQaG", "faqs_KDWjwK"]}